{"data":[{"date":"10:53 23/08","title":"\"Eden Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/eden-hazard-den-real-madrid-chi-la-chuyen-som-hay-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bermabeu ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard kh\u00f3 t\u1edbi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chuan-bi-gui-loi-de-nghi-cuoi-cung-vu-eden-hazard-180-195067.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real s\u1eafp g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i cho Hazard</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u1eb1m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mbappe \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (sau Neymar, 222 tri\u1ec7u euro).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Danny-Murphy-phat-bieu-ve-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Khi m\u00e0 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, n\u1ebfu Chelsea b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u0169ng cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Hazard chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, c\u00f2n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Danny Murphy tin Hazard ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bermabeu ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Murphy tin Hazard t\u1edbi Real ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu, nh\u01b0ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i, Hazard \u0111ang r\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c l\u00f2ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i cho Real. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i tin Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2019\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n t\u1eeb Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi The Blues hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2685","checkdouble":"195130"},{"date":"11:01 23/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Liverpool ch\u01b0a nh\u1ea3 Origi cho Dortmund","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/liverpool-muon-dortmund-mua-dut-divock-origi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi d\u00f9 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c hay sau 1 n\u0103m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Origi b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDivock Origi gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool t\u1eeb Lille v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng song ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 hi\u1ebfm khi ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2016/17 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Origi t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 43 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi \u0111a s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/liverpool-muon-dortmund-mua-dut-divock-origi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah r\u1ed3i c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino, Origi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Wolfsburg song c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 6 b\u00e0n sau 34 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i b\u1ed9 ba Mane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Daniel Sturridge, Adam Lallana, Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Rhian Brewster, Dominic Solanke hay Sheyi Ojo\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool-172-194245.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/7/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool-172-194245.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafp chia tay Liverpool</span><br>\r\n<span>Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho Origi ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ra gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Dortmund. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh trong v\u00f2ng 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m. Khi m\u00e0 Origi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n giao k\u00e8o v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh, Liverpool quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef quan \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Dortmund \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool xu\u1ed1ng thang. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Kop d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Danny Ings v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y song r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 anh t\u1edbi Southampton d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tham-hoa-thu-mon-chia-tay-liverpool-vao-cuoi-tuan-nay-172-194937.html\">Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n chia tay Liverpool v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-194914.html\">Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chinh-thuc-thanh-ly-hang-ton-klavan-172-194741.html\">Liverpool CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C thanh l\u00fd h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n Klavan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-194419.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2684","checkdouble":"195131"},{"date":"11:03 23/08","title":"V\u00ec sao M.U b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jurgen Klopp, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh</em> cho \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1eb7t ra. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n. 3 n\u0103m qua, Liverpool s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t song ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfc khi\u00ean th\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng mong manh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac m\u00e0 <em>ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Liverpool c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t</em> sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. Th\u1eadt v\u1eady, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham t\u1ea1i Wembley v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2017 t\u1edbi nay, The Kop l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Liverpool-thang-2-tran-EPL.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u201cr\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ef1ng b\u00f3ng\u201d nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u, song nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 mong manh nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u00f3m \u201cBig Six\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Liverpool, Klopp mang theo <strong>l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf, m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n song l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro</strong>. Nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 50 th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, toan t\u00ednh trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf nhoi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Goc-nhin-Nghich-ly-cua-Liverpool,-logic-cua-chien-thang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1eebng c\u00f3 l\u00fac The Kop \u0111\u1ea7y mong manh trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, <em>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i</em> v\u00e0 b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Klopp l\u00e0: \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ghi 3 b\u00e0n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ghi 4. H\u1ecd nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn binh c\u00f3 v\u0169 kh\u00ed kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp nh\u1ea5t, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf gi\u00e1p ra \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u0103ng hoa, Liverpool qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi li\u1ec1n t\u00f9 t\u00ec m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ch\u1ec9nh xong trang ph\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, The Kop c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<u>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c</u>. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t h\u1ea1 West Ham 4-0 v\u00e0 Crystal Palace 2-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 l\u1ea7n sau 2 tr\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hang thu Liverpool chac chan hon\" title=\"hang thu Liverpool chac chan hon\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/hang-thu-Liverpool-chac-chan-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Liverpool hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nLogic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1eafm l\u1ec7ch l\u1ea1c, thi\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn trong khi m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 (\u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c), b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League r\u1ed3i \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00ean y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd, ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. C\u1ea3 Real v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi \u201cbi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t\u201d t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp theo \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Klopp \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c</strong> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool. Trong tay \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn t\u00ean c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <u>Liverpool c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n</u>. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 mang t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t anh, Virgil van Dijk ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd tho\u00e1t pressing h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Alisson-cua-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Alisson g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n \"l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c\" Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Van Dijk, Joe Gomez ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u00e0 Crystal Palace, \u0111\u00e1nh tan ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nghi ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1 thay Dejan Lovren. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p nguy kh\u00f3, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Naby Keita c\u00e0y \u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 <em>nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Liverpool</em>. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng thay v\u00ec g\u1eddn g\u1ee3n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ng\u00e0y vui s\u1edbm t\u00e0n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi Liverpool ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t Liverpool c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m, th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111ang d\u1ea7n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn cho C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Liverpool \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League sau 28 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Th\u1ee9 7 n\u00e0y, v\u00f2ng 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Brighton tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):</strong>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&autoplay=false&urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho-172-194447.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n 1): Vua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-40-west-ham-khi-chiec-ao-khong-lam-nen-thay-tu-172-194355.html\">Liverpool 4-0 West Ham: Khi chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u1ea7y tu</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-palace-02-liverpool-172-195001.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-ly-do-tin-tuong-liverpool-se-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-172-195092.html\">Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Liverpool s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2683","checkdouble":"195132"},{"date":"10:53 23/08","title":"Fan M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 gi\u0103ng bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/2/12/ceo-cua-mu-nhuc-dau-vi-thanh-tich-cua-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward, v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nFan M.U kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Man United m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 thua thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng gi\u1eefa PCT Ed Woodward v\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jose Mourinho c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh, trong khi Ed Woodward l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y hay ho cho l\u1eafm. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho li\u00ean h\u1ec7 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward\" title=\"Ed Woodward \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Man Utd\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/2/12/ceo-cua-mu-nhuc-dau-vi-thanh-tich-cua-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Turf Moor c\u1ee7a Burnley t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Man United \u0111ang l\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ecb PCT ki\u00eam G\u0110\u0110H n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef <strong>&ldquo;ED OUT &ndash; LUHT&rdquo;</strong> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n, v\u1edbi \u00fd ngh\u0129a: <em>&ldquo;Ed Woodward c\u1ea7n ra \u0111i, Y\u00eau M.U nh\u01b0ng gh\u00e9t nh\u00e0 Glazer (Love United Hate Glazer).</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Man United, khi chi\u1ebfc chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 bay ngang SV\u0110 c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef &ldquo;Wrong One &ndash; Moyes Out&rdquo;. V\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, b\u00e0i to\u00e1n m\u00e0 Jose Mourinho c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-man-united-con-khong-bang-roma-172-195119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-man-united-con-khong-bang-roma.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-man-united-con-khong-bang-roma-172-195119.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Man United c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Roma</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Patrick Kluivert l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U, ch\u1ecdn AS Roma l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi cho c\u1eadu con trai.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dang-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-su-sup-do-cua-hang-thu-172-195058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/dang-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-su-sup-do-cua-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dang-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-su-sup-do-cua-hang-thu-172-195058.html\">\u0110\u1eb1ng sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton: S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y M.U ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2682","checkdouble":"195133"},{"date":"11:20 23/08","title":"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Willian cho Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/chelsea-doi-y-bat-ngo-muon-ban-willian-cho-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid mua Willian l\u1ea1i m\u1edf ra, theo Mirror Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Willian b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Braizl l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. M.U v\u00e0 Barca quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea m\u1edf c\u1eeda gi\u00fap Real Madrid mua Willian  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea m\u1edf c\u1eeda gi\u00fap Real Madrid mua Willian  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/23/Chelsea-mo-cua-giup-Real-Madrid-mua-Willian--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988, song Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 50, 53 v\u00e0 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Malcom.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian-180-192290.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Willian</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn, HLV Sarri tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Willian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid mua Willian l\u1ea1i m\u1edf ra, theo Mirror Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" title=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Willian-noi-ve-viec-chuyen-den-MU-o-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh ra b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Pedro, Morata v\u00e0 Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPedro \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua anh \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n, gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield v\u00e0 Arsenal. HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pedro, \u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Willian b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n anh cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. HLV Lopetegui v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Willian l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2681","checkdouble":"195136"},{"date":"11:11 23/08","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/goc-nhin-nghich-ly-cua-liverpool-logic-cua-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jurgen Klopp, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh</em> cho \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1eb7t ra. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n. 3 n\u0103m qua, Liverpool s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t song ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfc khi\u00ean th\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng mong manh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac m\u00e0 <em>ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Liverpool c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t</em> sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. Th\u1eadt v\u1eady, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham t\u1ea1i Wembley v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2017 t\u1edbi nay, The Kop l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Liverpool-thang-2-tran-EPL.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u201cr\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ef1ng b\u00f3ng\u201d nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u, song nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 mong manh nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u00f3m \u201cBig Six\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Liverpool, Klopp mang theo <strong>l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf, m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n song l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro</strong>. Nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 50 th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, toan t\u00ednh trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf nhoi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Goc-nhin-Nghich-ly-cua-Liverpool,-logic-cua-chien-thang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1eebng c\u00f3 l\u00fac The Kop \u0111\u1ea7y mong manh trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, <em>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i</em> v\u00e0 b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Klopp l\u00e0: \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ghi 3 b\u00e0n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ghi 4. H\u1ecd nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn binh c\u00f3 v\u0169 kh\u00ed kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp nh\u1ea5t, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf gi\u00e1p ra \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u0103ng hoa, Liverpool qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi li\u1ec1n t\u00f9 t\u00ec m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ch\u1ec9nh xong trang ph\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, The Kop c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<u>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c</u>. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t h\u1ea1 West Ham 4-0 v\u00e0 Crystal Palace 2-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 l\u1ea7n sau 2 tr\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hang thu Liverpool chac chan hon\" title=\"hang thu Liverpool chac chan hon\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/hang-thu-Liverpool-chac-chan-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Liverpool hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nLogic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1eafm l\u1ec7ch l\u1ea1c, thi\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn trong khi m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 (\u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c), b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League r\u1ed3i \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00ean y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd, ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. C\u1ea3 Real v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi \u201cbi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t\u201d t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp theo \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Klopp \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c</strong> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool. Trong tay \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn t\u00ean c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <u>Liverpool c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n</u>. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 mang t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t anh, Virgil van Dijk ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd tho\u00e1t pressing h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Alisson-cua-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Alisson g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n \"l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c\" Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Van Dijk, Joe Gomez ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u00e0 Crystal Palace, \u0111\u00e1nh tan ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nghi ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1 thay Dejan Lovren. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p nguy kh\u00f3, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Naby Keita c\u00e0y \u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 <em>nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Liverpool</em>. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng thay v\u00ec g\u1eddn g\u1ee3n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ng\u00e0y vui s\u1edbm t\u00e0n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi Liverpool ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t Liverpool c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m, th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111ang d\u1ea7n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn cho C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Liverpool \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League sau 28 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Th\u1ee9 7 n\u00e0y, v\u00f2ng 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Brighton tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):</strong>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&autoplay=false&urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho-172-194447.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n 1): Vua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-40-west-ham-khi-chiec-ao-khong-lam-nen-thay-tu-172-194355.html\">Liverpool 4-0 West Ham: Khi chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u1ea7y tu</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-palace-02-liverpool-172-195001.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-ly-do-tin-tuong-liverpool-se-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-172-195092.html\">Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Liverpool s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2680","checkdouble":"195138"},{"date":"11:20 23/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atalanta vs Copenhagen 01h00 ng\u00e0y 24/8 (Europa League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-atalanta-vs-copenhagen-01h00-ngay-248-europa-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atalanta vs Copenhagen l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 24/8 (V\u00f2ng playoff gi\u1ea3i Europa League/c\u00fap C2 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atalanta vs Copenhagen 01h00 ng\u00e0y 248 Europa League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atalanta vs Copenhagen 01h00 ng\u00e0y 248 Europa League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Atalanta-vs-Copenhagen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Atalanta vs Copenhagen</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>Atalanta vs Copenhagen: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atalanta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Serie A tham d\u1ef1 Europa League 2018/19 nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2. \u1ede v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y sau khi b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ebfn 8-0 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 3. \u1ede v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3, Atalanta v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Hapoel Haifa c\u1ee7a Israel v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng play-off.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Atalanta \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 9/10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Frosinone \u1edf tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Serie A 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Copenhagen l\u00e0 th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 8 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 BHL \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Copenhagen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111u\u1ed1i h\u01a1n Atalanta. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u1ea1i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n n\u00ean tin l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nAtalanta: Gollini, Masiello, Toloi, Palomino, Hateboer, Gosens, Gomez, de Roon, Freuler, Pessina, Zapata<br>\r\nCopenhagen: Olsen, Boilesen, Lueftner, Vavro, Bengtsson, Zeca, Kvist, Thomsen, Verbic, Santander, Sotiriou.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2679","checkdouble":"195139"},{"date":"11:32 23/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 23/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-2308.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 23/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2308 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2308 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2308-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adrien Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Le10Sport Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Leonardo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca chi 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro mua sao tr\u1ebb Argentina</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Leonardo Balerdi c\u1ee7a Boca. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ivan Rakitic b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng sau khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn PSG, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua sao Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City mua Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Barca quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marc Cucurella mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Blaugrana.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua sao tr\u1ebb Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua Adrien Rabiot. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 h\u01a1n 50 tri\u1ec7u&nbsp;Euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Rakitic cho PSG?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" title=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/liverpool-tranh-ivan-rakitic-voi-mu-trong-mua-he-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic cho PSG v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 125 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic cho PSG n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed ch\u1ecbu chi ra 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; Rafinha</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Rafinha ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Real Betis, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Man City mua Sergio Busquets</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sergio Busquets, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 500 tri\u1ec7u euro. Hi\u1ec7n Pep \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Dortmund l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch &quot;r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t&quot; Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paco Alcacer lot vao tam ngam cua Dortmund\" title=\"Paco Alcacer l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Dortmund\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/dortmund-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-paco-alcacer.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paco Alcacer l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Dortmund</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dortmund mu\u1ed1n mua Paco Alcacer c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1eafn anh v\u1edbi Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2678","checkdouble":"195140"},{"date":"11:34 23/08","title":"4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u qua, trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00edch, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 5-4-1. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a &ldquo;3 ch\u00e0ng l\u00ednh ng\u1ef1 l\u00e2m&rdquo; Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng &ndash; Duy M\u1ea1nh &ndash; \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0ng khi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t t\u00e0i &ldquo;s\u0103n t\u00e2y&rdquo;, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p n\u1ebfu \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, Mr. Park bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. \u00d4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a V\u0103n L\u1ee3i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, ho\u1eb7c xoay s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 sang 2 trung v\u1ec7. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn cho d\u00f9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain 4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain 4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Truoc-tran-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Bahrain-4-cau-hoi-can-giai-dap-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ai thay th\u1ebf H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 1 trong 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic, d\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qua 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng &ndash; m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay &ndash; L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain 4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nho-cay-bac-si-han-quoc-chua-tri-cho-hung-dung.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ebfm hoi ch\u01b0a th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o, gi\u00e0nh 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, Park Hang Seo th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 hy sinh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u00e0nh 1 su\u1ea5t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i). Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao cho chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cao qu\u00fd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 trong m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 11m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n chung cu\u1ed9c. Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Mr. Park \u0111\u00e3 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Olympic Bahrain m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch su\u00f4n s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain 4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/thay-tro-park-hang-seo-da-san-sang-dau-sung-o-vong-loai-truc-tiep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Li\u1ec7u B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c bay nh\u1ea3y trong tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 v\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi 1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat HAGL s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, c\u00f2n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb 2 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y n\u00f3i l\u00ean chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 trong tay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1995 &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ebfn 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng, trong khi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y trao cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain 4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Olympic-Viet-Nam-thang-Pakistan-Nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u0169ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u (m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain), ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/viet-nam-can-tan-cong-phu-dau-truoc-bahrain-292-195086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-can-tan-cong-phu-dau-truoc-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/viet-nam-can-tan-cong-phu-dau-truoc-bahrain-292-195086.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 g\u1ee3i \u00fd v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-195110.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-195110.html\">HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Samir Chammam tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2677","checkdouble":"195141"},{"date":"11:53 23/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Zorya vs RB Leipzig 01h30 ng\u00e0y 24/8 (Europa League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-zorya-vs-rb-leipzig-01h30-ngay-248-europa-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zorya vs RB Leipzig l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 24/8 (V\u00f2ng playoff gi\u1ea3i Europa League/c\u00fap C2 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Zorya vs RB Leipzig 01h30 ng\u00e0y 248 Europa League 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Zorya vs RB Leipzig 01h30 ng\u00e0y 248 Europa League 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Zorya-vs-RB-Leipzig.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zorya vs RB Leipzig</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>Zorya vs RB Leipzig: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng RB Leipzig \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng RB Leipzig v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp c\u1eeda tr\u00ean. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf RB Leipzig kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 \u1edf c\u00e1c m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd m\u1ea5t \u0111i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng Naby Keita \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u00f2n c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Werner, Forsberg \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u sa s\u00fat. \u1ede 2 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 3 Europa League, RB Leipzig \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Zorya, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ukraine kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u01b0ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3, Zorya \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra ch\u00fat b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua CLB \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Braga c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng l\u01b0u \u00fd l\u00e0 Zorya th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i hay khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi (th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1edfi m\u1edf c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cao. Zorya t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. 5/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, 2 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a RB Leipzig c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2676","checkdouble":"195142"},{"date":"07:25 23/08","title":"N\u00d3NG: Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean VTV6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nong-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-se-duoc-chieu-tren-vtv6.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1eeb VOV, \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam VTV s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 23/8.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean VTV6<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00d3NG Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00d3NG Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/NONG-Tran-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Bahrain-se-duoc-chieu-tren-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0vs Olympic Bahrain tr\u00ean VTV6</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 thao n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n h\u01a1n ASIAD, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y VTV \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng v\u0103n xin ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng ASIAD v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VOV. Hai b\u00ean \u0111ang tri\u1ec3n khai k\u00fd th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u0169ng ghi r\u00f5 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng, tr\u00edch d\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ghi r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n, gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng logo VOV b\u1edfi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng nguy\u00ean tr\u1ea1ng ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0i ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e8n c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1eaft qu\u00e3ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp s\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VTV s\u1ebd th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng. Kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u00ean ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ASIAD tr\u00ean k\u00eanh VTV6. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui h\u01a1n v\u1edbi NHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u2018xem l\u1eadu\u2019 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-duoc-khen-co-lua-cau-thu-tre-tot-hon-thai-lan-168-195100.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, c\u00e2y b\u00fat c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Fox Sports Asia \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-bahrain-chi-ra-3-ngoi-sao-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195099.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Bahrain ch\u1ec9 ra 3 ng\u00f4i sao nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Bahrain t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2675","checkdouble":"195106"},{"date":"08:12 23/08","title":"HLV Barcelona ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/18/ernesto-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-cong-nghe-var.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barcelona c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>VAR ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, VAR (c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd video) ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, n\u00f3 d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, VAR c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng. La Liga m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/Ernesto-Valverde-phat-bieu-ve-cong-nghe-VAR-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0i nghi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 VAR v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. V\u00e0 HLV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd video \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Barca. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00f3 c\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5 hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n VAR l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 n\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t nhanh, \u00edt khi b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n. C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng cho t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng xung quanh v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR t\u1ea1i La Liga s\u1ebd ra sao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19, Barca \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Deportivo Alaves ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-bat-ngo-ra-yeu-sach-voi-barca-180-195091.html\">Ivan Rakitic b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/sao-tre-barca-lap-hattrick-vao-luoi-real-madrid-328-195081.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Barca l\u1eadp hattrick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-muon-mua-adrien-rabiot-176-195061.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ea1nh tranh Rabiot c\u00f9ng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ac-milan-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-rabiot-voi-barca-180-195051.html\">AC Milan gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao PSG v\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-phu-nhan-mua-cillessen-vao-thang-1-172-195029.html\">Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua sao Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2674","checkdouble":"195107"},{"date":"07:52 23/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 23/8: Son Heung-min c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn M.U \u2013 Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-238-son-heungmin-co-the-gop-mat-o-dai-chien-mu-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea th\u0103ng hoa, Arsenal ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London \u0111\u1ec1u thay t\u01b0\u1edbng, v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri k\u1ebf nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Antonio Conte \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Arsenal chia tay Arsene Wenger sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 Unai Emery.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, thay t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn. T\u00ednh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u n\u00f3i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh \u1edf Chelsea sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Arsenal tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 v\u1eabn l\u1eadn \u0111\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ashley Cole nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Arsenal vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn derby cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua khi Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Emery, Ashley Cole \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB LA Galaxy c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111eo tay:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri nh\u01b0ng theo c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00e2m th\u1ea7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd, c\u00f2n t\u00f4i th\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. S\u00e1u \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi Arsenal, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Emery. H\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u00fat n\u00e0o khi \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i m\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm, ch\u01b0a quen thu\u1ed9c khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Arsene Wenger \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates trong khi Chelsea h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn St. James&rsquo; Park l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Newcastle v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-vs-arsenal-tien-dao-alvaro-morata-172-194782.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/140159-4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-chelsea-vs-arsenal-tien-dao-alvaro-morata-172-194782.html\">Chelsea th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Derby London: Ng\u00e0y Sarri h\u1ed3i sinh Morata</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u00e3 xem Diego Costa h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea vi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\">Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2673","checkdouble":"195108"},{"date":"08:34 23/08","title":"Ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil ch\u1ec9 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/Nguoi-Bayern-Munich-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-chia-tay-doi-tuyen-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 mang nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00faa r\u00ecu d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMesut Ozil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, Ilkay Gundogan \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i l\u1edbn trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, Recep Tayyip Erdogan &ndash; nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau m\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi Ozil v\u00e0 Gundogan c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m. M\u1ed7i khi kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch gay g\u1eaft. S\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ozil v\u00e0 Gundogan n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i chung cho World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Nguoi-Bayern-Munich-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-chia-tay-doi-tuyen-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u00f2n Ozil th\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc d\u1eabn t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJurgen Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Borussia Dortmund l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan. HLV c\u1ee7a Liverpool tin r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3. &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng tin tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sai l\u1ea1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a&rdquo;, Klopp n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1ecf nh\u1eb7t lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i bay v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 l\u1edbn lao b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4ng minh c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e9m l\u1ea1i v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb m\u1ea5t tr\u00ed th\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t to ti\u1ebfng trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 Ilkay Gundogan v\u00e0 Emre Can. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t (ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c). V\u1eady ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u?&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/carragher-chi-ra-2-mat-xich-yeu-nhat-trong-doi-hinh-arsenal-172-195090.html\">Carragher ch\u1ec9 ra 2 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-dang-phai-chien-dau-cho-tuong-lai-o-arsenal-172-195031.html\">Ozil \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-dau-emery-van-vui-vi-ozil-biet-nghe-loi-172-194797.html\">Arsenal thua \u0111au, Emery v\u1eabn vui v\u00ec Ozil... bi\u1ebft nghe l\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-bao-ve-thoi-luoi-phong-ngu-cua-ozil-172-194723.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ozil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-unai-emery-nhac-mesut-ozil-tich-cuc-tham-gia-phong-ngu-hon-172-194714.html\">HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafc Mesut Ozil t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2672","checkdouble":"195109"},{"date":"08:05 23/08","title":"HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Samir Chammam tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/flf1534947226.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Samir Chammam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng chia s\u1ebb: &quot;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain. T\u00f4i mong h\u1ecd s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bahrain \u0111\u00e3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 0-6 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E Asiad 2018. Tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng&nbsp;Chammam b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00f3, Bahrain \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 n\u00e9t qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng Chammam cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u1eady n\u00ean, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea5y r\u00f5. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb ng\u1ee3p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn, n\u00ean m\u1edbi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo HLV&nbsp;Chammam, Olympic Bahrain \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Malaysia 3-2 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Song nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Chammam c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp d\u00f9 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/11/22/bao-nuoc-ngoai-nhan-dinh-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-malaysia-hy-vong-olympic-viet-nam-se-tien-xa-tai-asiad-2018-168-195102.html\">HLV Malaysia hy v\u1ecdng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Malaysia Ong Kim Swee \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-don-hung-tin-ve-nhan-su-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain-168-195101.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n hung tin v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng vui v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2671","checkdouble":"195110"}]}